American Express and Resy make no representations or warranties regarding the availability of reservations, events, and/or experiences, which are subject to availability and the discretion of the applicable restaurant. In-person and over-the-phone reservations (i.e., without using Resy) may be accommodated, subject to space and availability limitations. Please include any dietary restrictions, food allergies, or requested accommodations in your Resy profile. American Express and Resy are not responsible for any dietary restrictions, food allergies, or for not being able to accommodate such restrictions or allergies. You are responsible for any purchases or fees associated with your reservation(s). Platinum Nights by Resy reservations are intended for personal use only and cannot be
 transferred, redistributed, or otherwise sold to another individual or entity. Must be 21 years of age to consume alcoholic beverages. Please drink responsibly.
