The Platinum Nights by Resy benefit provided through Resy is intended solely for personal use by eligible American Express Card Members. To maintain fairness and prevent abuse of this benefit, Resy reserves the right to investigate through reasonable means any account that is suspected of using the Platinum Nights by Resy benefit in a manner that violates these Platinum Nights by Resy terms and conditions or Resy Sites’ Terms of Service (including, but not limited to, “Usage Guidelines” that are provided therein). If upon such review, Resy determines, based on its reasonable discretion, that any of the aforementioned terms have been violated, Resy and American Express reserve the right to enforce appropriate consequences, including suspension or termination of access to the Platinum
